          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The value of the property is a constant that indicates the current orientation of the device. This value represents the physical orientation of the device and may be different from the current orientation of your applicationâ€™s user interface. See ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIDeviceOrientation",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " for descriptions of the possible values.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The value of this property always returns 0 unless orientation notifications have been enabled by calling ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIDevice/beginGeneratingDeviceOrientationNotifications()",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
